roup_UK_500x.jpg?v=1724927162 320w" width="2000" height="1125" alt="Dubai Stopover Itinerary: Adventures Await on Your Short Stay - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Dubai Stopover Itinerary: Adventures Await on Your Short Stay - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-dBmyGf kIntMx pf-108_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-109_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by BlackWhaleMedia via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-111_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">I’m considering researching what other fun activities we can do in Dubai. My mum has already looked into some things and maybe even booked a few activities for us, but I still want to learn more about what I might like to do. Perhaps I’ll check out what the hotel offers, too. They have a lovely swimming pool, and since I love swimming, that’s definitely on my list!</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-113_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-md:5px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bVHBsO cYbKeb pf-114_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kAkozD kgiAhT pf-115_ pf-heading-1-h3">What should we do?</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Top_Attractions_During_a_Dubai_Layover_Make_the_Most_of_Your_Time_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1724927620" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Top_Attractions_During_a_Dubai_Layover_Make_the_Most_of_Your_Time_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1724927620 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Top_Attractions_During_a_Dubai_Layover_Make_the_Most_of_Your_Time_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.jpg?v=1724927620 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Top_Attractions_During_a_Dubai_Layover_Make_the_Most_of_Your_Time_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.jpg?v=1724927620 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Top_Attractions_During_a_Dubai_Layover_Make_the_Most_of_Your_Time_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1724927620 320w" width="2000" height="1335" alt="Top Attractions During a Dubai Layover: Make the Most of Your Time - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Top Attractions During a Dubai Layover: Make the Most of Your Time - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-dBmyGf kIntMx pf-117_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-118_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by AydinovKamran via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-120_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">One of the reasons we’re stopping in Dubai is to help us adjust to the time difference between the Philippines and England. The time zones are different, and sometimes, it’s hard to get back into the swing of things when we travel. So, we’ll use this time in Dubai to rest and get ready for the final leg of our journey home.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-122_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-md:5px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bVHBsO cYbKeb pf-123_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kAkozD kgiAhT pf-124_ pf-heading-1-h3">Looking forward to Dubai</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Short_Stay_in_Dubai_Adventures_and_Cultural_Experiences_Await_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1724928386" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Short_Stay_in_Dubai_Adventures_and_Cultural_Experiences_Await_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1724928386 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Short_Stay_in_Dubai_Adventures_and_Cultural_Experiences_Await_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.jpg?v=1724928386 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Short_Stay_in_Dubai_Adventures_and_Cultural_Experiences_Await_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.jpg?v=1724928386 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Short_Stay_in_Dubai_Adventures_and_Cultural_Experiences_Await_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1724928386 320w" width="2000" height="1332" alt="Short Stay in Dubai: Adventures and Cultural Experiences Await - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Short Stay in Dubai: Adventures and Cultural Experiences Await - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-dBmyGf kIntMx pf-126_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-127_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by tampatra via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-129_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">I’m still sad about leaving the Philippines, but thinking about Dubai is helping me feel better. Who knows? I might end up loving it there. I’ll let you all know how it goes in my next blog. </p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-7a9a" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-cVzzKN jdAbCJ pf-131_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-YysaK jCVJYo"><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-132_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:5px;--s-sm:10px;--s-md:5px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bVHBsO cYbKeb pf-133_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/IMG-20230413-WA0064_7c81edc6-a94d-4e5a-8338-930a2834337d.jpg?v=1705928795" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/IMG-20230413-WA0064_7c81edc6-a94d-4e5a-8338-930a2834337d.jpg?v=1705928795 1536w" width="1536" height="2048" alt="Dubai Layover Guide: Exploring the Best of Dubai in a Day - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Dubai Layover Guide: Exploring the Best of Dubai in a Day - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-dBmyGf kIntMx pf-134_ pf-image-1"/></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6